user_prompt: With a longing to experience flight, I jump out of an airplane with a parachute. For a brief moment, I freefall completely through the sky. After a short while, I deploy the parachute and feel the jolt as it opens.
prompt_variant: Eager to soar, the skydiver jumps from the aircraft and relishes the freefall until the parachute deploys with a firm jolt.
